.TP
.BI \-c \ CONFIG_DIR\fP,\fB \ \-\-config\-dir \ CONFIG_DIR
Specify config directory. Defaults to "/etc/sara"
.TP
.BI \-S \ SECURITYFS\fP,\fB \ \-\-securityfs \ SECURITYFS
The mount point of the securityfs. Defaults to
